text.tspan: If you did not reach rotation speed by taxi way "G" : Abort Takeoff
If there is there is enough runway available : Abort Takeoff
If below 500 ft : Slight turn, try to land on runway 28 or aim for the Highway 116
If above 1000ft : Turn 180 deg to come back and land on 06R or 06L
Check traffic by lowering the nose
